<template>
    <v-app id="inspire">
        <v-navigation-drawer
        v-model="drawer"
        app
        color="green lighten-4"
        >
        <v-container>
            <v-list-item>
                <v-list-item-avatar>
                <!-- <v-img src="https://randomuser.me/api/portraits/men/78.jpg"></v-img> -->
                <v-icon size="30">mdi-account-circle</v-icon>
                </v-list-item-avatar>

                <v-list-item-content>
                <v-list-item-title>John Leider</v-list-item-title>
                </v-list-item-content>
            </v-list-item>

            <v-divider></v-divider>

            <v-list dense>
                <v-list-item
                v-for="item in items"
                :key="item.title"
                link
                >
                <v-list-item-icon>
                    <v-icon>{{ item.icon }}</v-icon>
                </v-list-item-icon>

                <v-list-item-content>
                    <v-list-item-title>{{ item.title }}</v-list-item-title>
                </v-list-item-content>
                </v-list-item>
            </v-list>
        </v-container>
        
        </v-navigation-drawer>

        <v-app-bar app color="green lighten-4">
        <v-app-bar-nav-icon @click="drawer = !drawer"></v-app-bar-nav-icon>

        <v-toolbar-title>My Reserva</v-toolbar-title>
        </v-app-bar>

        <v-main>
            <!-- <empresas-component></empresas-component> -->
            <agendar-component/>
        </v-main>
    </v-app>
</template>

<script>

import AgendarComponent from './AgendarComponent.vue'
import EmpresasComponent from './EmpresasComponent.vue'

export default {
  components: { EmpresasComponent, AgendarComponent },
    name: "InicialComponent",
    
    data: () => ({
         drawer: null,
         items: [
          { title: 'Home', icon: 'mdi-view-dashboard' },
          { title: 'About', icon: 'mdi-forum' },
        ],
    }),
}
</script>
<style scoped>
    .v-main {
        padding: 10px 10px !important;
    }
</style>
